.TP 8n
.B -Interactive
.br
.RS
Specify that \*(n) should ask the user for confirmation
before deleting each file.
Answer the question
.I yes
to delete the file, or
.I no
to keep the file.
You can also answer
.I all
to delete the file and all that follow, or
.I none
to keep the file and all that follow.
.PP
Defaults to the user's
.I delete_file_preference
if not specified, see
.IR aeuconf (5)
for more information.
.PP
If \*(n) is running in the background,
the question will not be asked,
and the files will be deleted.
.RE
